title: Should This Bert Show Member Feel Guilty About Calling The Cops On Their Neighbor?
description:
Over the weekend, Romeo went through a scary experience in his neighborhood. His neighbor's dog attacked him! It's not the first time an incident like this has happened. Because of this, he called the cop on his neighbor. But now, he feels guilty.
